OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud and
OL,6,Fpatchy rain may move into the far west
OL,7,Fat times overnight. Otherwise dry with
OL,8,Fclear spells, but some mist and fog
OL,9,Fpatches may develop, especially in the
OL,10,Feast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FWestern areas continuing to
OL,13,Fsee some cloud and patchy rain at
OL,14,Ftimes, especially in the afternoon.
OL,15,FElsewhere, any fog clearing allowing
OL,16,Fsome bright or sunny spells to
OL,17,Fdevelop. Feeling mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
